            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "在岸人民幣兌美元收升22點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">在岸人民幣兌美元官方收6.9628，較上日官方收盤價漲22點，較上日夜盤收盤漲12點。</p>\n</div>",
