        {
            "title": "龍旗科技首掛以高於招股價3.55%收市 每手賬賺110元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">今日登場的卜新股龍旗科技(09611)，高開後迅速回順，但全日穩守招股價31元之上，收報32.1元，較招股價高3.55%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"龍旗科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/Longcheer-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"龍旗科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/Longcheer-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">龍旗科技官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">以該股1手100股計，認購並獲配每手賬面賺110元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該股今早以35元開市，最高曾見36.86元，較招股價高18.9%，最低價31.22元也高於招股價0.71%；全日成交8.37億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">龍旗科技A股(603341.SH)今日則逆市向下，收壣48.16元人民幣，跌0.91%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15603518-%e9%be%8d%e6%97%97%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e9%a6%96%e6%8e%9b%e4%bb%a5%e9%ab%98%e6%96%bc%e6%8b%9b%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b93-55%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82-%e6%af%8f%e6%89%8b%e8%b3%ac%e8%b3%ba110%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/Longcheer-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 16:16:12",
