            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股窄幅現跌9點  泡泡瑪特反彈逾半成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股午後窄幅，恒生指數現跌9點或0.04%，報26575，恒生科技指數跌3點或0.07%，報5742點，恒生國企指數跌29點或0.32%，報9093點，成交1988.36億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"泡泡瑪特(微博圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/574x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250429_PL_pop_source_web_56.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"泡泡瑪特(微博圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/574x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250429_PL_pop_source_web_56.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">泡泡瑪特(微博圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">泡泡瑪特(09992)午後升幅擴大，最高見207元，升6.48%，現升5.86%，報205.8元，為表現最佳藍籌股。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">地產股向好，九倉置業(01997)升4.73%，報26.58元 ; 新鴻基地產(00016)升3.9%，報114.5元; ，升幅藍籌股中居第二、三位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">百度發布文心大模型5.0版，升3.38%，報158.9元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國人壽(02628)跌3.21%，報31.92元，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 京東健康(06618)跌3.07%，報64.75元，跌幅居第二位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">南山鋁業(02610)挫7.84%報63.5元，成交入20大，公司折讓6.4%配股籌20億元，現價跌破配股價。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15603364-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e7%aa%84%e5%b9%85%e7%8f%be%e8%b7%8c9%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b3%a1%e6%b3%a1%e7%91%aa%e7%89%b9%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88%e9%80%be%e5%8d%8a%e6%88%90",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-6.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 15:24:13",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "窄幅爭持 滬指收升5點 深指升0.5% 金融板塊偏軟",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地A股午後氣氛稍微改善，滬市股指仍好淡爭持，深市股指則喘穩轉升。石油行業板塊依然強勢，金融行業則持續偏軟。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/油價FB-1-2-2-1-1-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-1-1-1-2-1-1-1-1-2-3-2_source-ap_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/油價FB-1-2-2-1-1-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-1-1-1-2-1-1-1-1-2-3-2_source-ap_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指高開9點後於初段原本一直向好，最高見4140點，漲23點，但在早市中段動力卻突降，漸呈好淡爭持，半日已倒跌收場，全日低位4109點，跌7點，午後大致在4110點至4123點之間12點上落；滬指最後收報4122點，升5點或0.14%，成交1.2萬億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指今早亦呈反覆偏軟格局，初段最高見14374點，升121點，早市中後段反覆倒跌，但最多只跌31點，報14223點，午後回復上升軌，只是升幅局限在75點以內；深指收報14327點，轉升71點或0.5%，成交1.49萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數微升不足1點或0.01%，以4723點收市；創業板指數收漲33點或1.01%，報3328點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金融行業板塊主要股份跌多升少，內險與大型銀行股均受壓。中國平安(02318)A股(601318.SH)跌1.6%，報64.8元；中國太保(02601)A股(601601.SH)也跌1.82%，報43.1元；中國人壽(02628)A股(601628.SH)更跌2.13%，報46.9元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">4大國有商業銀行A股全線向下，表現最遜色的農業銀行(01288)A股(601288.SH)跌2.16%，報6.81元；跌幅最小的中國銀行(03988)A股(601988.SH)則跌0.56%，報5.3元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Shutterstock圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20230719_FI_source_licensed_01288_shutterstock_704.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Shutterstock圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20230719_FI_source_licensed_01288_shutterstock_704.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Shutterstock圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國際石油市場供應趨緊有利支持油價，A股市場的石油行業板塊乘勢跑出。石化油服(01033)A股(600871.SH)收漲8.79%，報2.6元。「三桶油」全線向上，中國石化(00386)A股(600028.SH)升4.2%，報6.21元；中海油(00883)A股(600938.SH)升4.12%，報31.82元；中國石油(00857)A股(601857.SH)升1.5%，報10.15元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">水泥股午後升勢亦擴大，金隅集團(02009)A股(601992.SH)漲停板，報2.05；海螺水泥(00914)A股(600585.SH)也升2.92%，報23.96元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15603332-%e7%aa%84%e5%b9%85%e7%88%ad%e6%8c%81-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%875%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%870-5-%e9%87%91%e8%9e%8d%e6%9d%bf%e5%a1%8a%e5%81%8f%e8%bb%9f",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-8.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 15:16:07",
